---
title: Spinach & Ricotta Ravioli, Bacon & Mushroom Sauce with Balsamic Rocket & Parmesan
description: Pillowy spinach and ricotta ravioli, swimming in a luscious, creamy mushroom sauce and topped with bacon and a generous sprinkle of Parmesan - this dish is pure comfort in every bite. Top it with a tangy balsamic rocket salad for a zingy kick!

